OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FPeople running out of      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fenergy credit every 10     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fseconds                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Citizens Advice has called for a ban on
OL,6, energy companies "forcing" customers   
OL,7, onto prepayment meters because they are
OL,8, struggling to pay bills.               
OL,10,FThe charity estimates that 3.2 million 
OL,11,Fpeople across Britain ran out of credit
OL,12,Fon their prepayment meter last year,   
OL,13,Fthe equivalent of one every 10 seconds.
OL,15,FSome have meters installed, while      
OL,16,Fothers have smart meters automatically 
OL,17,Fswitched to prepayment mode.           
OL,19,FMinisters said energy firms must offer 
OL,20,Fextra help to struggling customers.    
